application

Class Movie

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.Movie

  • public class Movie
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines the movie data model and provides methods and fields used when configuring table views. The string and int properties are created to enable referencing to a particular data element.
    Author:
    Aakash
